locations: New York City, New York, USA
imdb.plot outline: When Jake loses his job that he hates a whole new world opens up. He dives into the sea of odd jobs and daily work to find his new passion. He searches for what he truly wants to do in life by taking as many random jobs as possible. The jobs he picks are mostly dead end jobs, but he works to justify their importance with his girlfriend, his friends, and ultimately himself. Jake works to keep the hope alive in a city that suddenly has no boundaries, but also, no safety net.
imdb.title: Work, in Progress
plot: Losing your dead end job, opens up a whole new world of opportunities, what if you don't know what to do next?

When Jake loses his job that he hates a whole new world opens up. He dives into the sea of odd jobs and daily work to find his new passion. He searches for what he truly wants to do in life by taking as many random jobs as possible. The jobs he picks are mostly dead end jobs, but he works to justify their importance with his girlfriend, his friends, and ultimately himself. Jake works to keep the hope alive in a city that suddenly has no boundaries, but also, no safety net.
